messages.subject: Bedtime try out
messages.msgSnippet: Hi ladies bedtime last night was interesting... Steve and I put a movie for the kids and started to watch one ourselves (thank goodness for vcr s)... Zak
messages.messageBody:
Hi ladies

bedtime last night was interesting... Steve and I put a movie for the
kids and started to watch one ourselves (thank goodness for vcr's)...
Zak watched his movie and Max kept coming out and running around in
front of the tv, which was fine because before the movie was on for 10
mins DH was asleep on the couch (he's been working long days lately)...
So I put the kids to bed and we went to bed and I read while peace
reigned in the house. I guess I'll just keep trying.... The good news
is that we all got a great night's sleep. I was asleep the latest at
10pm (LOL).... Where have my younger days gone when I could stay up all
night

Dawn (who's going to be 43 on Friday)
Tucson, AZ
